Package modelServer

Class ModelManager

java.lang.Object
modelServer.ModelManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Model
public class ModelManager extends Object implements Model
The ModelManager class implements the Model interface and manages the application's data and logic. It provides methods for creating users, logging in, managing folders and exercises, and handling user interactions with the system.
